En servlet Ã¤r en javaklass som hanterar requests och responses.
Den mappas till en viss URL (Under webappens web context) genom Servlet Mappings. See src/web.xml.

Build with:
javac -cp lib/servlet-api.jar src/ExampleServlet.java
mkdir -p WEB-INF/classes
mv src/ExampleServlet.class WEB-INF/classes/
cp src/web.xml WEB-INF/
zip -r webapp.war WEB-INF

Run with:
cp webapp.war ${TOMCAT_HOME}/webapps
${TOMCAT_HOME}/bin/catalina.sh run